messages.message: These aren’t very technical people, i’d be shocked if they knew anything about APIs
What is the risk of someone having that many fields?

i don’t think we’ve ever tested extraction with that many fields, so the model accuracy may be unknown

for example, if they upload a new doc to the project, we’ll run extraction for all fields at once for that new doc

the only other thing would be the slowness in the UI that you mentioned, i think
